Thus far, skalds and their TL have never &quot;aggressively&quot; pushed Mythic for improvement to the class, because most of the skalds and the player base felt that the class was well balanced.<br>
<br>
Though melee changes were long overdue, and I am more than happy to see a better survivability for &quot;pure&quot; tanks, there are a few points that need to be considered :<br>
- With all the melee class boosts, hybrids, and particularly skalds risk to significantly lag behind pure melee class (I say particularly skalds because of the 1.5x spec and no shield means we don't benefit from the parry and block improvements as much as the other 2.0x shield speccable hybrids). The &quot;freebie&quot; purge is particularly crippling for a class that relies heavily on its mez, the cheaper IP too ...<br>
- Though I do agree that pure melees needed more love than hybrids, all of the fighter classes have melee combat as a primary focus, including skalds, so they are all affected by the &quot;melee problems&quot;  that were supposed to be fixed in this version : insane AE CC spells, insane nuking damage, inability to defend or assault keeps efficiently, vulnerability to range and stealth ... Hybrid's spell abilties help mitigate some of those problems, but I still believe the whole melee vs. (assassins, casters, CC) issue is essentialy shared by all of the fighter classes, pure or hybrids.<br>
So if the fixes are limited to the pure tank classes, it will be quite a let down.<br>
<br>
So I hope the announced hybrid love will help balancing things a bit. If not, we'll need to start asking for improvements in a more pressing manner. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/uwoodeethorndawg.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Woodee Thorndawg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/6/02 10:00:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=276.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 1.53a</span><hr size=1> I just discovered this board through a link on the VN boards which I just started reading recently.  I really hope it is helpful communication.<br>
<br>
Has anybody brought up the fact that we are the bard and chant class of our realm combined?  It seems to me that we have to fill two roles.  I already don't attack anything but casters and healers until there is no choice but to go after the other realms tanks/hybrids.  Now they will all have purge and IP and parry/block us more and we will miss more.  So the CC then go after the casters strategy will be less effective because all the tanks will purge then we have to kill them twice (IP).  I see this as a huge problem on Galahad as the Hib nukers wipe us quick if we don't take them out and the Albs seem to have endless healing if we don't get to them.  Being tied up with the tanks at the start of pretty much every battle is going to put us at a distinct disadvantage.  So if they are going to put this in, they need to realize that we have to be competitive melee for our realm while still providing the bard/chant abilities.  Reduce our RA points.  Not as much as the tanks but maybe somewhere in between.  Also make our shouts and chants more effective especially when it comes to the end and pwr they use.  I've read a lot of posts here with good ideas so I won't add to that.  I just think that they continue to tweak the other classes while we get no improvements.  Because of our importance and multiple roles in our realm, we need to stay a dominant class.  And I didn't even get into the fact that we have to continue to provide solid melee since we are in the melee realm.  I just don't want to become a class that is needed just for speed and I feel that's what we are becoming especially with the changes in 1.53.  I hope they are aware and considering the affect this will have on us.<br>
<br>
Woodeq 50 Skald, Galahad <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/upranzer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pranzer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/17/02 11:42:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=276.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 1.53a</span><hr size=1> I agree with you Kjeld<br>
